text: My experience at the Johor Traditional Chinese Medicine Acupuncture Specialist left a profound impression. Their team of traditional Chinese medicine practitioners not only possesses exceptional skills but also emphasizes personalized care for patients. Every treatment made me feel their genuine concern, creating a comforting experience throughout the therapy. It is truly a reliable Chinese medicine institution, and I will continue to choose Johor Traditional Chinese Medicine Acupuncture Specialist. Highly recommended.

Worst acupuncture sessions I have ever attended in my life.

This so called professor is a joke. Zero relief, plenty of pain and he doesn't even understand my problem.

At one point, he was bending my ligament backwards and when I screamed in pain, he asked the nurses what was going on and they had to explain to him and he said "Oh".

Ridiculous. Utter waste of money. Avoid.
